RMEnsure Zap 1.44 Error This version of ZapEmail requires Zap 1.44 or later
Set ZapEmail$Dir        <Obey$Dir>
Set ZapEmail$Path	<ZapEmail$Dir>.<Zap$Country>.,<ZapEmail$Dir>.UK.,<ZapEmail$Dir>.

Set ZapEmail$Taglines   <ZapEmail$Dir>.Taglines
Set ZapEmail$Signatures <ZapEmail$Dir>.Signatures

Set Zap$TMF_Email       <ZapEmail$Dir>.TMF

| The sprites file is selected in an *IconSprites-like way
Set ZapEmail$Scripts    ZapEmail:Scripts
Set ZapEmail$Sprites    ZapEmail:Sprites
Set ZapEmail$Templates  ZapEmail:Templates
Set ZapEmail$Menus      ZapEmail:Menus